column5: DAM: the trouble with getting rid of this page is that Planning & Trans doesn't really have a page geared toward small business. Developers can easily navigate planinng/zoning processes, but small businesses don't have that ability. ESD serves as liaison and we need a way for the web to reflect this "service" of ours; and also a convenient "one-stop" location for businesses to understand who they need to meet, what their regulations/ requirements might be... that's what ESD's small business strategy is all about -- maybe there's a way to consolidate this with (business resources) or (business incentives & assistance)
DAM: a lot of the small business questions we get are from mobile food vendor startups or food carts; this is helpful information to keep available on the website.  in some format.
